Function reference

KHIS Metadata

Download metadata information related to the organisation units, categories and data elements

get_organisation_units_metadata()
Get Organisation Units Metadata
get_category_options_metadata()
Get Category Options Metadata
get_data_elements_metadata()
Get Data Elements Metadata

Cervical cancer screening data

Downloading data related to cervical cancer screening

get_cervical_screened()
Retrieves Cervical Cancer Screening Data
get_cervical_hiv_screened()
Retrieves Cervical Cancer Screening Data on HIV Positive Women
get_cervical_positive()
Retrieves Cervical Cancer Screening Data with Positive Results
get_cervical_treated()
Retrieves Cervical Cancer Precancerous Treatment Data

Breast cancer screening data

Downloads data related to breast cancer screening

get_breast_cbe()
Retrieves Data for Clinical Breast Examinations (CBE) Conducted
get_breast_mammogram()
Retrieves Data for Mammograms Conducted

Authorization Credentials

Take and securely store the KHIS authorization credentials

khis_cred()
Sets the KHIS Credentials
khis_has_cred()
Are There Credentials on Hand?

Target population

Fetches the target population for the different screening programs

get_cervical_target_population()
Get Cervical Cancer Screening Target Population
get_breast_cbe_target_population()
Get the Clinical Breast Examination Target Population
get_breast_mammogram_target_population()
Get Mammography Target Population

KHIS Analytics

Download data from KHIS analytics table

get_analytics()
Retrieves Analytics Table Data from KHIS
